<para>The way you build D++ varies from system to system. Please follow the guide below for your OS:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="buildlinux" kindref="compound">Building on Linux</ref></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="buildwindows" kindref="compound">Building on Windows</ref></para>
