</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="buildopenbsd" kindref="compound">Building on OpenBSD</ref></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="warning"><para>Note that you most likely don&apos;t need to build D++ from source if you&apos;re on Linux or Windows. We offer prebuilt binaries for these platforms and are listed in package managers! Check the downloads in the releases section on github. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
